relevant_findings.HEENT: Extraocular movement intact, pupils equal, round, reactive to light, mucous membranes moist.
relevant_findings.neck: No lymphadenopathy, jugular venous pressure within normal limits.
relevant_findings.respiratory: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezing or rhonchi (note wheezing on admission).
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Obese, small umbilical hernia present. Bowel sounds present. Soft, non-tender, non-distended.
